      "Set Weekly Rapport Goals: Create micro-goals like: \u201cTalk to someone I don\u2019t know,\u201d \u201cReconnect with a colleague,\u201d or \u201cResolve a misunderstanding using curiosity and warmth.\u201d Track and reflect on these weekly.",
